channel.title: Runescape cheating...dead?
channel.description:
I've been lurking these here forums for too long... learning about popping and pushing those stacks and endless brain-killing BCEL. Big words like Deobfuscating and stuff I have no idea about like making a loader and hacking the client's canvas. But the forums seem dead now... Is there no longer a way to learn about cheating in RS? Is everything Katnieks worked for dead? From the beginning: Nick Sherlock, google, then SCAR and Aryan, up until Moparscape and Powerbot. Is there some other forum people have migrated to? If so, where?
BTW, I heard no one uses BCEL for bots anymore, stuff like ASM and ModScript. True?

In case you’re still a little confused… What you did was kind of weird, don’t do that. If you were hoping to add him as a friend on facebook, make a real friend instead.
